  "instructions": [
    "In a blender or food processor, puree the tamarind pulp and 1 cup of water until smooth.",
    "In a medium saucepan, whisk together the miso paste and 2 cups of water until smooth.",
    "Bring the miso mixture to a simmer over medium heat.",
    "Add the vegetable broth, coconut milk, and ginger to the saucepan.",
    "Return the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the rice noodles to the saucepan and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the soy sauce, honey, and lime juice.",
    "Season the broth with salt to taste.",
    "Ladle the soup into bowls and garnish with cilantro."
